# Deployment — SCNAT Digitalisierungsportal

## Architecture

- **Repo**: git@github.com:silvanpoltera/scnat-digitalisation-platform-PROD.git
- **Live URL**: https://platform.poltis.ch
- **VM**: Google Cloud, Ubuntu 22.04, 1 vCPU / 1 GB RAM + 2 GB Swap
- **SSH**: `ssh silvanpoltera@34.148.41.234`
- **App path on VM**: `/opt/scnat-portal-prod`
- **Process manager**: PM2 (process name: `scnat-api`)
- **Reverse proxy**: Nginx with SSL (Let's Encrypt, auto-renew)
- **Backend**: Express on port 3001 (proxied via Nginx at `/api/`)
- **Frontend**: Vite SPA served from `/opt/scnat-portal-prod/dist`

## Deploy Command

After committing and pushing to `origin/main`:

```bash
ssh silvanpoltera@34.148.41.234 "cd /opt/scnat-portal-prod && bash deploy.sh"
```

`deploy.sh` runs: `git pull`, `npm install`, `npm run build`, `pm2 restart scnat-api`.

The build takes ~3 minutes due to limited VM RAM (swap is configured).

## Security Rules — MANDATORY

- **NEVER** commit or log secrets (`.env`, JWT_SECRET, passwords)
- **NEVER** expose SSH keys, IPs, or credentials in code or comments
- **NEVER** run `git push --force` on this repo
- **NEVER** modify `.env` on the VM without explicit user approval
- **NEVER** open additional ports on the VM firewall
- **NEVER** disable or weaken SSL, CORS, or cookie security settings
- Cookie config: `secure: true`, `sameSite: 'strict'`, `httpOnly: true`
- CORS: restricted to `process.env.CORS_ORIGIN` (production domain only)
- All API routes require authentication unless explicitly public

## Verification After Deploy

Run this to confirm everything is healthy:

```bash
ssh silvanpoltera@34.148.41.234 "pm2 status && curl -s -o /dev/null -w 'HTTPS: %{http_code}\n' https://platform.poltis.ch/ && curl -s https://platform.poltis.ch/api/auth/me"
```

Expected: PM2 `online`, HTTPS `200`, API returns `{"error":"Nicht authentifiziert"}`.

## Local Development

```bash
cd scnat-portal-prod
npm run dev:all        # Frontend (5173) + Backend (3001)
```

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `deploy.sh` | VM deployment script |
| `server-setup.sh` | One-time VM provisioning |
| `nginx.conf` | Reference Nginx config (live config managed by Certbot) |
| `.env.example` | Environment variable template |
| `data/*.json` | Application data (committed, used by both frontend and backend) |
